headline: Could Buying O'Reilly Automotive Stock Today Set You Up for Life?
summary: One of the best traits of O'Reilly's business is that it faces durable demand from customers, regardless of macro conditions.  O'Reilly Automotive (NASDAQ: ORLY) has done nothing but take care of its shareholders.  There's a reason why O'Reilly's stock performance has been so magnificent.
